# AI Assistant Rules (Antigravity & others)

The following rules must be strictly followed when working in this repository. Detailed instructions for each skill are separated into individual files located in the `skills` directory. Before modifying any part of the project covered by a skill, you MUST read the corresponding skill file.

## Available Skills

1. **Asset Version Bumping** (`skills/asset_versioning.md`)
   - Read this skill file when modifying ANY static files (`.css` or `.js`). It explains the required cache-busting procedure in `index.html`.

2. **Auto-Tagging New Words** (`skills/auto_tagging.md`)
   - Read this skill file when adding new Greek vocabulary words to `js/words/lessons.js`. It explains the necessary commands to run to automatically tag the new words.
